INSTALL - Anteater Chess

Requirements:
  Linux (tested on UCI EECS servers: Bondi, Laguna, Crystalcove, Zuma, Balboa, Doheny)
  GCC 9.0 or later
  GNU Make
  OpenGL and X11 (pre-installed on UCI servers)

To build from source:
  tar -xvzf Chess_Alpha_src.tar.gz
  cd chess
  make

To run:
  bin/chess

To run tests:
  make test

To clean build files:
  make clean

To uninstall, just delete the directory:
  rm -rf chess/
